      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this pristine, showroom-quality vehicle. Meticulously maintained and presented in impeccable condition, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly turn-key masterpiece that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 48900.0,
